questions.quote: Well y'know about the tongue thing, y'know, and how I told you about my likes and my dislikes...
Pheebs, if this guy keeps closing down all of our favorite places, where are we gonna eat?!
I know that you're new at this, but this is completely unacceptable bath decorum.
No! No! It's just that he gave me three tickets and there are six of us!
So! So we've got to go upstairs and have a lot of sex to prove them wrong!
Oh, great! Just what you want for a new house with infants. Bird feces.
